data.description: This charming 1921 bungalow is your ticket to small-town living located in La Salle, a quaint community south of Greeley, with easy Hwy 85 access. This cozy home boasts two bedrooms and two baths.  Sunlight fills every corner, creating a warm atmosphere. Step in through the enclosed porch - a perfect spot for your morning coffee. The open living and dining areas offer space for gatherings. A back porch doubles as a sunroom or office space and laundry room.  Outside you will find a heated detached oversized garage and a large carport.   All this nestled on a 9500 sq ft fully fenced lot with alley access. NO HOA means freedom for parking your RV, boat or other toys.  Huge yard for gardening or outdoor entertaining your options are endless!  This gem boasts numerous upgrades: Including a metal roof, new furnace and central air, new windows, modern interior & exterior paint, new primary 3/4 Bath, new back deck, and upgraded flooring.  Don't miss this opportunity!
